==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: deers-ear
<hw>deer's-ear</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>any of various tall perennial
herbs constituting the genus <gen>Frasera</gen>; it is widely
distributed in warm dry upland areas of the US Pacific states.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> columbo, American columbo, deer's-ears, pyramid
plant, American gentian.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

